Product name: Mid Century Camel Brown Leatherette Suitcase with Travel Stickers
Description:
LARGE 1950s BROWN SUITCASE WITH STICKERS
(Scroll down below story to read complete item description/condition)
Abercrombie Reynolds stood on the train station platform, steam from the idling locomotive drifting up into the overhead lights. He was awaiting the 9:45 PM to Toledo holding what was left of his life in his brown Stylite suitcase.  His stomach was alarmingly close to his throat as he anxiously contemplated the variety of scenarios that might play out in Toledo. 
Abercrombie was down to his last 3.23 but he had his ticket and he had a job. Now he just had to prove that he was the best duplex-crossmember salesman in the U. S. of A. He had promised Acme Crossmember Company of Toledo, Ohio that he was THE man to pull them out of their three-year sales slump. Now he had to deliver. 
The conductor called out, "Aaaaaaaall Aboard for Toledo, Ohio...aaaall aboard." 
The locomotive let out a long sigh of steam which broke the tension he was holding in. "Yes, I CAN do it, Yes, I"m their man," he said aloud as he gripped his suitcase and stepped up into the train car...onto his track of destiny.

ITEM DESCRIPTION:
Here's a fun, circa 1950s suitcase ready for decorating or storage. It measures 24" X 18" and tapers slightly from 8" at the bottom to 7" on the handle end. It is constructed out of fiberboard with a camel brown colored faux leather vinyl covering. The case features brass-tone hardware/trim and a matching brown handle. The interior is lined with beige/brown tweed fabric and features two dividers and brown vinyl strap. We added some reproduction vintage travel labels with a western theme- Las Vegas, Grand Canyon, Wyoming Air and Pan Am Alaska Clipper. 
CONDITION:
This suitcase has some travel scuffs and and nicks to the exterior but no major structural issues. The metal hardware has some wear to the finish and a few specks of rust. The latches work well (no keys included) and the handle is firmly attached. The interior fabric lining has a few light water stains but no foul odors. This case lays flat when open.
SHIPPING:
Flat shipping rate of 29.95 to anywhere in the lower 48 USA states. It may ship via FedEx Ground so please provide a physical shipping address if different than your mailing address (no PO Boxes). We can also ship it to Alaska/Hawaii/US Territories but it will run a little more for shipping by USPS Parcel--Convo us for a shipping rate prior to purchasing for those locations.
STORE POLICIES NOTE:
When you purchase this item you are agreeing to our store policies. Please take a moment to review them.

___________________________________________________________________________
LEGGINGS SIZING CHART *****PLEASE READ BEFORE ORDERING*****
Our leggings follow sizing with a specific national children’s brand (please private message us to find out which). 
OUR FIT: Our default style for boys is a “regular fit” this fit is not meant to baggy or relaxed, although it may be so on slim babies.  Our default sizing for girls is “slim” which is shorter in the leg and more fitted through the thigh/leg.  We also make a third style: “husky” this style is the same length as our “regular fit” but has a bigger waist and more relaxed fit in the thighs.  “Husky” will be necessary for babies that are very above average in size for their age.  “Regular fit” will be appropriate for average to slightly above average children, although please note that our lengths all run on the longer side. 
***Whether you have a boy or a girl, any of our sizes may be appropriate for your mini depending on their size/shape and your preferred fit.  None of our leggings are pre-shrunk and there will be slight shrinkage, please keep this in mind when ordering.*** 
UNDERSTANDING MEASUREMENT: “Length” here is from top of waistband to bottom of the ankle.  “Waist” is the measurement of the circumference of the elastic waistband.  Our elastic waists stretch up to 2” for comfort.  When you measure for your mini’s waist measure around the belly button when they are sitting for standing, not laying down unless the baby is not old enough to sit.  The best way to measure length is not on your baby, rather measure a pair of leggings that fit them on a flat surface from waistband to ankle.

Description:
Dogs are truly man's best friend!  Our loyal companions who leave their paw prints on our hearts.  Why not celebrate your best friend by giving them their own personalized placemat to place under their dog food bowl! Product name: Bunny Fur Dog Tug Toy
Description:
Bunny bumper tug toy for dogs.  My dogs go crazy for these!  If your dog isn't into playing tug, they will be now!  
The tug is approximately 8" long (the rabbit portion, varies slightly based on the size of each rabbit pelt) and can be made either with a flat nylon web handle  (1st picture) or a braided poly rope handle (2nd picture).   Made with real rabbit fur pelt, which I purchase locally in the US, which are marked with made in Spain.  
Pictured is the sable coloring, but I also have white pelts in stock.  
NOTE: Dogs should not be left unattended with toy, they will eat the fur.  These toys are meant for interactive play between you and your dog, they are not for entertaining your dog unattended.  The toy is a rectangular cut of genuine rabbit pelt, stuffed with polyfill, which has been fused to interfacing to make it stronger, but the fur is very easy to pull out if the dog is left to destroy the toy.  This toy should be used to play tug or fetch with your dog, and then should be put away and not left with the dog.  Of all the toys I sell, this one is definitely the most easily destroyed by dogs, but as dogs absolutely LOVE this toy, it's very popular for those who want toys as motivation for agility and other dog sports, obedience training, or just bonding and having fun with your dog.  
Please allow up to one week for these to ship as they are custom made.

Product name: Premium Viking Beard Oil Sampler Pack | Sample Kit
Description:
Fires of Freyja Beard Oils are made using Organic Oils of Jojoba, Argan, and Sweet Almond Oil with the addition of nourishing Vitamin E Oil, Essential Oils and Premium-Grade, Skin-Safe Fragrance Oils. This combination will soften and tame your beard, while nourishing your skin and your soul. 
This boxed sample pack is 3-1/2" x 3-1/2" and includes 4 premium beard oils in sample-size amber bottles (1/8 oz) in the scents listed below and also includes a description card printed front and back for gift giving.
SUNSTONE
Crystals known as Iceland spar were called Sunstones (sólarsteinn) by the Vikings and were used to locate the sun when it was obstructed from view for navigation at sea.  This scent embraces the fragrance of Viking longboats on their voyages to explore new lands and embodies the refreshing essence of salty sea air and kelp, with light eucalyptus and wood scents. The scent of The Mariner!
HEIDRUN
Scent inspired by Heiðrún, the magical goat in Norse mythology, who eats the leaves from the life tree Yggdrasil. She then converts the leaves to mead for all of the dead warriors of Valhalla.  This is a premium beard oil scented with the warmth of amber and honey. The scent of Valhalla! 
BERSERKER
Ber·serk·er – (noun):  An ancient Norse warrior who fought in a wild frenzy, often without armor, wearing only wolf or bear skins.  This scent is the embodiment of the legendary warriors who inspired fear in their opponents by mere sight alone.  Berserker is an animalistic scent with notes of musk, spiced ale, earth and bonfire.  The scent of The Warrior!
SACRIFICE
Sacrifice is directly influenced by the HISTORY Channel Vikings episode of the same name (S1E8), which portrays the ceremonies held every nine years at Uppsala (Sweden) to honor the Gods.  This is a premium beard oil lightly scented with notes of forest, earth, smoke and incense creating an ancient ritualistic aura.  The scent of The Seer!
***If you have any allergies to specific scents or oils, please inquire before making a purchase.

Autumnblooms Healing Salve is made with only the finest, organic ingredients. This eczema salve works beautifully on both infants and adults. It is gentle enough for faces and even a baby's bottom. Description:
Scoop, count, balance, drop, giggle, repeat. 
Little hands will love this all natural Busy Bag that satisfies a toddlers need to scoop, pour, dump and repeat. Count the balls as they are scooped from the bowl and dumped into the cute wooden bucket with a sturdy metal handle. Set the scoop aside and dump the balls from one container to the other or opt to use fingers and strengthen hand muscles. 
This natural Busy Bag is sure to delight. Pack the wooden pieces in the muslin pouch and tote with you to waiting rooms, restaurants or bring out the Busy Bag to give yourself a little time to get chores done. 
This Busy Bag is small, the wooden balls are about the size of a grape. I would recommend this activity for children 3 years of age or older. It is great for little hands and strengthening fine motor skills. Please supervise your child during play. 
Contents: 
1 bucket with metal handle standing 2” tall 
1 bowl 2.5” wide and 1.25” tall 
1 small wooden scoop measuring 3” long 
6 small wooden balls .75” (about the size of a grape)
 
-all wooden pieces are sanded and then sealed with organic beeswax and olive oil 
An adorable muslin bag will contain your Busy Bag items. Open the bag, dump out the contents and use the bag as a work mat. This will create an easy to manage workspace and will make cleanup a breeze. 
More wooden Busy Bags: 
https://www.etsy.com/shop/busybagFUN?ref=hdr_shop_menu§ion_id=19303032
 
_________________________________________________________________________________________
Why Busy Bags? 
- Do you need some time to make dinner, clean the house or make a phone call? Give your child this teacher approved Busy Bag and keep them entertained- allowing you to get work done.  
- They are portable.  Whip them out while waiting at the doctor’s office, a restaurant or during church. Also, Busy Bags can travel with you to make time go by a little more smoothly.
- Busy Bags create a great distraction for when you need to redirect unwanted toddler behaviors. 
- Busy Bags are wonderful non-tech activities that strengthen early development skills such as: fine motor, hand-eye coordination, visual discrimination, counting, sorting and oral language.
- Most games improve fine motor skills which create the foundation children need before they learn handwriting. As a teacher I know the importance of fine motor development and see a direct correlation between a child’s fine motor control and their handwriting abilities.
- Most importantly, they are FUN!  
These Busy Bags are thoughtfully created by me, a kindergarten teacher, who knows the value of promoting early childhood skills and the long term benefits they create. 
This listing contains small items that are not suitable for children who still put things in their mouth. Parental supervision required.

Product name: Baby Toy - New Baby Gift - Personalized Baby Rattle - Waldorf Baby - Baby Wooden Toy
Description:
Ready to ship!  
To place your order, add the rattle to your cart and leave a note at check out with your baby's name.  
Our customers have asked us for years to craft personalized wooden baby rattles and finally, after many attempts at perfecting what we feel is a great rattle with no parts that are glued or can pop off and be a choking hazard, we are happy to introduce our one of a kind Cake in the Morn baby rattle!
Your rattle is engraved using a hot woodburning tool.  No glue, no ink, no markers, no chemicals, no toxins, no dies--all natural wood for your little one. 
Made from untreated 100% American hardwood from Maine and measuring 4.5" long, our rattles are crafted entirely of wood.  Each part of the rattle is hand sanded and assembled with care.  Personalize your rattle with your choice of decorations on the solid wood top as well as with your babies name on the handle.  Finally, you can choose the color of the base of the rattle to fit your babies personality and style.  The rings on the rattle are what creates the magical noise that keeps your baby smiling and laughing.  Your rattle is then sealed with our homemade beeswax seal.
**Please note--the top of the rattle is not hollow with beads inside.  It is a solid piece of wood**

This wedding set has been oxidized to create a dark patina accenting the texture and pattern.

This listing is available with your choice of diamond ring only or diamond ring with matching band (shown in the photos of this listing)...you can select your option prior to adding this to your shopping cart.  
**Please be aware that oxidizing is a natural process. On this ring set I have accelerated this process. Over time, with wear, the oxidized finish will enhance and change...becoming darker in the deep crevices and lighter on the high areas of the texture...and will be unique to the wearer.
The diamond used in the creation of this ring comes from legitimate sources not involved in funding conflict. My trusted supplier of this diamond guarantees that it is  conflict free and takes every reasonable measure to help prevent the sale of conflict diamonds in accordance with the Kimberley Process.

Product name: Remote Controlled Lights! 100 Fairy Lights, 17-foot (5m) wire strand.  Choose battery-operated or plug-in string lights with remote control.
Description:
This product is a string of 100 warm white Fairy Lights on a thin copper wire that is powered by 3 AA batteries, 3 C Batteries, 2 D Batteries, any USB port, or a 110V wall plug (for USA and Canada).  All of these products come with a remote control.
This item is small and great for enhancing home decor and party decor crafts. This product comes in copper or silver wire color.  There are 100 Warm White Fairy Lights on each strand, and the strands are 17-feet long. (5 meters)
The remote for the battery powered options includes the following buttons:  On, Off, 4-hour timer, 6-hour timer, 8-hour timer, candle flicker, no flicker, dim, and bright.
The AA Battery Packs are roughly 2.9" by 1.9" by 0.75".  The Waterproof AA Packs are rough 3.3" by 2.5" by 0.9".  Life of AA batteries depends on the batteries, but it is roughly 15 to 20 days when set to 6 hours per day.
The C Battery pack is 3.3" by 3.3" by 1.5".  It uses 3 C batteries.  The battery box is clear, and it is not waterproof.  C batteries will last about 5 times as long as AA batteries.
SOLD OUT - The D Battery Pack is 4" by 3" by 1.5". It uses 2 D batteries. The lights and the box are waterproof. D batteries will last about 10 times as long as AA batteries.
The USB option plugs into any USB port.  This product has 7 feet of lead wire, and a remote control.  You can power these lights with your computer, your laptop, your car, or best of all with a wall plug that has a USB port.  (Select the plug-in option if you want us to provide the wall plug.)  For our non-USA, non-Canada customers, this would be your best option if you want plug-in lights.  Just add a local USB power plug to this product, and you are good to go!
The plug-in option uses 110V AC power. It uses an American style plug attached to the USB product described in the previous paragraph.  There are 2 USB ports on each plug-in module.  This plug-in option is not designed for outdoor use.  You can operate 2 sets of USB lights from one plug-in and with one remote.
When the timers are set, the lights come on at the same time each day. Batteries are not included with the batter pack options.

Product name: Flower Ponytail Holder- Hair Accessories- Hair Ties- Elastic Hair Ties-
Description:
Beautiful sturdy Floral patterned, half round by 1 inch wide brass is soldered atop a tube which holds a very smooth, round, sturdy, high quality elastic made to last and last. Plated with a thick anti-tarnishing sterling silver or copper, oxidized to bring out the intricate detail, hand satined and lacquered to insure it will never tarnish. No special care is required. Amazingly lightweight
. 
Works perfectly on normal to the thickest of hair usually with a single loop. 
Your choice of three different satin ox finishes
Brass ox
or
Copper Ox
or
Sterling Silver Ox
HINT: Slip it on your hair first in the proper position, then twist the elastic from underneath your pony and loop over your hair.  If you feel you need to tighten it more, take it off, slip it back on, and then do a "double twist" or even a "triple twist" underneath your pony before you loop over your hair.  You DO NOT need to make a new full loop.  Just adding a second or third twist before you loop over your hair will take up the slack and make it nice and tight for those girls with thinner or silky hair. This will also add to the life of the elastic.
   
Shipped in a Velveteen Drawstring Pouch
